#: app_conf/templates/app_conf/about.html:406
msgid ""
"\n"
"            SecBoard is an integrated cybersecurity platform that brings "
"together all essential security management \n"
"            functions in one place. From risk assessment to incident "
"response, from compliance tracking to security \n"
"            awareness training - everything you need for comprehensive "
"security management.\n"
"            "
